<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Document Disapproved</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Dear {{ requestedBy }},</p>
    <p>
      We regret to inform you that your document
      <strong>{{ documentName }}</strong> has been disapproved on {{
      disapprovalDate }}.
    </p>
    <p><strong>Reason for disapproval:</strong> {{ disapprovalReason }}</p>
    <p>
      Please review the provided feedback and resubmit your document after
      making the necessary changes.
    </p>
    <p>You can view the project details by clicking the link below:</p>
    <p><a href="{{ projectLink }}">View Project</a></p>
    <p>Thank you for your understanding.</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br />The Approval Team</p>
  </body>
</html>
